rows.label: qev041203_MSG0001
rows.name: Phew! This should be far enough.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0002
rows.name: Prone at door only said "inside," so this must count.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0003
rows.name:
Being surrounded like this is little bit scary,
but shipment not going to deliver itself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0004
rows.name: ...Delivery complete! Next stop, home![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0005
rows.name: Stop.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0006
rows.name:
Client not approved goods yet.
You are poor merchant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0007
rows.name: Nuwha?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0008
rows.name: Eeep! S-so sorry, friend![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0009
rows.name:
Mumun did not see any boss-types around,
so was just heading back to entrance to get someone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0010
rows.name: I am boss. I check goods. You wait.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0011
rows.name: ...Bah! Trick! This is trick![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0012
rows.name: Er, is something wrong, friend?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0013
rows.name:
I am not friend! You are CHEAT! 
I order three times usual amount! Where is rest?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0014
rows.name:
WHAAAAAT?! Mumun never hear anything about
increased order size![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0015
rows.name: Silence![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0016
rows.name: You are bad merchant. Now my men go hungry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0017
rows.name:
Hungry Prone are poor workers.
This mistake will cost me fortune![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0018
rows.name: You will fix this, little cheat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0019
rows.name:
Gaaah! W-well then, how about Mumun take this
shipment back, verify order, and return withâ€”[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0020
rows.name:
You make this up right NOW!
Or I make up difference with Nopon flesh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0021
rows.name: Bwaaa ha ha ha ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0022
rows.name: EEEEEEEEP![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0023
rows.name:
*ahem* Mumun think now is time for you to shine,
friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0024
rows.name:
Protect Mumun! But do so in business-appropriate,
non-trade-relationship-hurting, peaceful sort of way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0025
rows.name: Negotiate! Make all okay![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0026
rows.name: That why Mumun brought friend here in first place.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0027
rows.name:
And now is time for friend to earn money that Mumun
never technically agree to pay.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_JNK0010
rows.name: Compromise

rows.label: qev041203_SEL0011
rows.name: Offer to track down the remaining items.

rows.label: qev041203_JNK0020
rows.name: Fight

rows.label: qev041203_SEL0021
rows.name: Resolve the situation with force.

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0028
rows.name:
Friend is serious? That 14 more kiweggs according to
ridiculous demands of Prone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0029
rows.name:
Kiweggs are huge pain in rump to gather,
and Mumun not going to pay extra for all that work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0030
rows.name: Friend really think we should do it anyway?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0031
rows.name:
Granted, that may be the only way for Mumun to get
out of here without becoming lunch...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0032
rows.name: All right! Mumun and friend will go find kiweggs![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0033
rows.name:
F-friend cannot really mean to take on this many of
them at once![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0034
rows.name:
Insanity! Madness! Zero chance of survivability!
...Mumun take no responsibility for this plan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0035
rows.name: Is friend still sure?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0036
rows.name: ...All right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0037
rows.name:
Mumun will hide in corner and stay faaar away from
suddenly bloodthirsty friend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0065
rows.name:
You STILL don't have them? Graaaaaaagh!
We are hungry! Bring 14 kiweggs or Nopon will pay![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0066
rows.name: We may even eat Earth alien. Now go![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0038
rows.name: Finally back?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0039
rows.name:
A-always pleasure to see best clients of Mumun!
Meeeeh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0040
rows.name: Silence! Have you brought goods or not?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0041
rows.name: ...Not bad. This will keep Prone fed for while.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0042
rows.name:
Yes, which is wonderful! So then, about the balance of
payment owed...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0043
rows.name: Balance? Bah![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0044
rows.name:
You brought too little. You are cheat.
There is no balance. I owe nothing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0045
rows.name:
B-b-but be reasonable! Finding that many kiweggs
nearly killed poor Mumun![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0046
rows.name: Then get order right next time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0047
rows.name: You still have life, cheat. Be grateful.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0048
rows.name: Nr...nrrrh...NRRAAAAAAAUGH![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0049
rows.name:
Now Mumun MAD! This last time Mumun ever do
business here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0050
rows.name:
This is scam, and Mumun not stand for it one
minute longer![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0051
rows.name: Little cheat may regret that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0052
rows.name:
The day merchant let customer win is last day
in career of merchant![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0053
rows.name: You won't sell? You are sure?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0054
rows.name: EXTREMELY sure![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0055
rows.name:
Then we take by force. Raid your caravan.
Claim all we desire.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0056
rows.name: Whaaaaaaaat?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0057
rows.name: You will not sell. We have no choice.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0058
rows.name: Hrrrrrrf...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0059
rows.name: Naaaarrrrrrgh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0060
rows.name: Oh ho ho ha ha hurf hurf hurf![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0061
rows.name:
Joking! Mumun was joking. Of course Mumun want to
keep selling to best Prone friends ever.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0062
rows.name: Good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0063
rows.name:
Mumun look forward to next order of friends.
Th-thankful that today was such wonderful transaction.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041203_MSG0064
rows.name: Oh ho ho ha ha hurf hurf hurrrrrf...[ST:wait ]
